{
  "name": "@huo15/openclaw-enhance",
  "version": "5.7.3",
  "description": "火一五·克劳德·龙虾增强插件 v5.7.3 — config-doctor：启动期诊断 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 陷阱配置（缺失 agents.defaults.compaction.reserveTokensFloor / model maxTokens 占 contextWindow 一半以上）解决 'Context limit exceeded' 高频反馈，只读不改配置，给可粘贴 fix 命令 + enhance_config_doctor 工具按需诊断。继承 v5.7.2 hardening + v5.7.1 hot-fix + v5.7 transcript-search + v5.6 工具分层 + 三层记忆协调。",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "index.ts",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": [
      "./index.ts"
    ],
    "build": {
      "openclawVersion": "2026.4.11"
    },
    "compat": {
      "pluginApi": ">=2026.4.11"
    }
  },
  "bin": {
    "openclaw-enhance-setup": "./scripts/setup.sh"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "openclaw",
    "plugin",
    "enhance",
    "memory",
    "safety",
    "agent"
  ],
  "author": "jobzhao15",
  "license": "MIT",
  "peerDependencies": {
    "openclaw": "^2026.4.22"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@sinclair/typebox": "^0.34.49",
    "better-sqlite3": "^11.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/better-sqlite3": "^7.6.0",
    "typescript": "^5.5.0"
  },
  "files": [
    "index.ts",
    "openclaw.plugin.json",
    "src/**/*",
    "templates/**/*",
    "scripts/**/*"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://cnb.cool/huo15/ai/huo15-openclaw-enhance"
  }
}
